{"tid":1823786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查：本港財務及會計界人士普遍對本港今年經濟悲觀","createTime":"2020-01-14T03:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T03:23:23.000Z","uid":226984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0bdf9abe34f3fce195f8b9421b6cf636e0ad2001","tid":1823786,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"特許公認會計師公會香港分會去年11月至12月初的調查顯示，受訪220名財務及會計界人士，對本港今年經濟表現相當悲觀，當中76%受訪者預計經濟表現差或非常差，只有2%認為表現好或非常好。<br />\n<br />\n40%受訪者預計經濟負增長，受訪者認為，對經濟最大負面影響首要因素是香港社會不穩，比例逾80%，其次是中美貿易糾紛，排第三為樓價及租金高企。<br />\n<br />\n另外，調查顯示，有逾20%受訪者認為粵港澳大灣區對本港各行業有正面影響，但逾60%認為沒有甚麼影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502673-20200114.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502673-20200114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHMwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=7070dfd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502673-20200114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=df03ec05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502673-20200114.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}